.deft-cache/

# vbrief/.eval/ tracking governance (#1144, N4 of #1119).
# Hybrid policy from the Current Shape comment on #1144:
#   - candidates.jsonl       -> gitignored (operator-private triage
#                               decisions; re-derive via
#                               `task triage:bootstrap` on a fresh
#                               clone). #845 Story 2 + #915.
#   - summary-history.jsonl  -> gitignored (operator-private
#                               observability; not load-bearing for
#                               any decision).
#   - scope-lifecycle.jsonl  -> gitignored (operator-private
#                               scope-lifecycle audit decisions;
#                               D1 / #1121). Per-operator demote
#                               stream; sharing would conflate
#                               operators' demote timing across the
#                               team.
#   - decompositions/        -> gitignored (local story-decomposition
#                               draft scratch; generated child story
#                               vBRIEFs live in lifecycle folders via
#                               `task scope:decompose`).
#   - doctor-state.json      -> gitignored (per-machine `task doctor`
#                               throttle state gating the 24h/4h
#                               re-probe window; #1308 / #1464). Local
#                               to each clone; never committed.
#   - slices.jsonl           -> TRACKED (team-shared cohort records
#                               produced by slicing skills; see
#                               #1132 / D13).
# See vbrief/.eval/README.md for the full policy + merge=union
# rebase note.
vbrief/.eval/candidates.jsonl
vbrief/.eval/summary-history.jsonl
vbrief/.eval/scope-lifecycle.jsonl
vbrief/.eval/decompositions/
vbrief/.eval/doctor-state.json
